{"tid":2181879,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"單兵用品拋磚引玉！","createTime":"2020-08-31T02:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T14:09:39.000Z","uid":370186,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"799a93966271a779fda4cda38b82b4020e0689bf","tid":2181879,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"最近睇多咗啲軍品 想吓連登有冇ching可以講多啲<br />\n咁就等我拋磚引玉！ (有部份唔想打字copy咗網上嘅資料) <span class=\"red\">同埋有錯請指正！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">1.防彈板</span><br />\n<br />\n好多人以為有件防彈背心就可以防彈 但其實最緊要都係塊板<br />\n<br />\n有分軟板同硬板 <span class=\"red\">(我唔太清楚軟板希望有ching可以幫我講)</span><br />\n<br />\n軟板就係NIJ lllA以下採用高性能纖維如尼龍、芳香族聚酰胺（例如著名的凱芙拉）或者超高分子聚乙烯（或稱迪尼瑪）即係防彈衣出邊嗰啲布啲friend <br />\n尼龍唔係普通尼龍係Denier Nylon（俗稱彈道尼龍）<br />\n1000D、900D～係佢啲規格 有興趣就自己上網睇吓唔多講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APSyxh7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPSyxh7.jpg&h=c325cd10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n硬板就係lllA級以上 通常用鋼鐵、聚乙烯、陶瓷整，出面再如多層布，防彈插板嘅表層工藝有很多種，一般分為兩類：聚脲塗層和防水布外層。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9FcNQH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9FcNQH.jpg&h=e2bf4ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有分防彈等級通常用美國標準 NIJ <br />\nⅠ級、ⅡA級、Ⅱ級、ⅢA級、Ⅲ級、Ⅳ級<br />\n咁我就貼圖唔太多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqoJUvX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqoJUvX.jpg&h=22cee1da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBjhevX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBjhevX.png&h=5530dcc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有分唔同形狀，要配合返件防彈背心<br />\n仲有分曲面同埋平面 曲面就符合返啲人體工學 平面就真係平啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMmrSmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMmrSmi.jpg&h=66170618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有有啲硬板佢有寫住不能單獨使用，咁你就要買返相應尺寸嘅軟質防彈內襯放埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n有分多次使用單次使用～<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">2.戰術背心</span><br />\n<br />\n戰術背心通常用高強度布料即係上面講嗰啲整<br />\n<br />\n個本體會有魔術貼同埋molle系統 即係一格格嗰啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kM5TxrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkM5TxrZ.jpg&h=d73adf4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰術背心種類有好多種，下邊幅圖嘅戰術背心只係為咗增加攜帶彈藥的數量，方便戰術動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TqasBUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqasBUW.jpg&h=252568b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗帶太多彈匣通常5個夠用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OR9heJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOR9heJt.jpg&h=1cbad7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幅圖係啲袋嘅種類，我見幾好用就借咗黎用，唔使理啲價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mavcN4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmavcN4a.jpg&h=50529ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰術背心最緊要唔好帶太多，但係你嗰次要用嘅就夠<br />\nhold on 有幾樣嘅記住要帶彈匣回收袋、子彈袋，因為如果真係要上戰場唔係好似打機咁隨手扔咗個彈匣，子彈袋就係放未入彈匣嘅子彈因爲會冇咁晒位等安全嘅時候就可以慢慢入彈 fa pack 止血帶 軍刀呢三個就唔多講<br />\n<br />\n好似仲有個快速解除系統可以講，不過如果你要知嘅話代表你都要買，咁你買完就可以自己試吓玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">戰術頭盔</span><br />\n<br />\n有分防彈定唔防，有啲為咗輕便所以係碳纖頭盔，碳纖頭盔因為唔使留子彈撞擊之後變形嘅位置所以會比較接近頭部<br />\n<br />\n戰術頭盔最高嘅防彈級別係NIJ IIIA 不過如果你想再勁啲可以喺出邊加多層甲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqDxU5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqDxU5b.png&h=64ac58af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔同品牌會有唔同戰術導軌系統<br />\n而家普遍都係下面依種<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TdNJ0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TdNJ0d.jpg&h=0ef49b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前邊仲有用嚟裝光學用具嘅底座<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xBLvGN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xBLvGN.jpg&h=7a8a3917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你前邊裝咗夜視鏡，咁你後面就要加裝返一個類似加重包咁嘅嘢，唔係好記得個專用名詞，佢仲可以用來整理你啲線<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多配件例如對講機耳筒，面罩，戰術電筒，識別燈，偽裝布 <br />\n我就唔講咁多直接放低條片，係普通話，但佢講得幾好 佢條片就係開箱文但係其實有講好多關於戰術頭盔基本嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Omr9mLFnuFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOmr9mLFnuFc&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoGdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=4fc9a83e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Omr9mLFnuFc</a><br />\n<br />\n呢三樣嘢我都係好基礎咁樣講，所以希望啲識嘢嘅人唔好屌得咁大力"},{"pid":"ec663fc36ffc356f4ad8dd3d7c5d508795b9d838","tid":2181879,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbdd209190bc82476b5fdc628488e918f122e7c","tid":2181879,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec663fc36ffc356f4ad8dd3d7c5d508795b9d838","tid":2181879,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:24:55.000Z","msg":"唔好笑我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adda346ad10a342c218689731a873c496be58a8","tid":2181879,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:43:16.000Z","msg":"哭啊 我咁俾心機寫都無人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8185bf5bb377412631721a97402ca42154861515","tid":2181879,"uid":366493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"有呀寫緊"},{"pid":"cc36095236ca8ad1abe76c441a9c45b54b96ee24","tid":2181879,"uid":366493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"我睇完 你係想買嚟玩 着上身？<br />\n有關 避彈衣 頭盔 影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ef3D_91MVMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fef3D_91MVMM&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoGdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=b9e89d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ef3D_91MVMM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FGTXzNVhKyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFGTXzNVhKyo&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoGdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=af104c0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FGTXzNVhKyo</a>"},{"pid":"97df955bf5742d967d7662b715144ecfe69241f1","tid":2181879,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"又來裝備撚着到成個美軍咁<br />\n打交都唔夠古惑仔狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 唔好引人笑啦屌你"},{"pid":"eda971f9e0ae0f723941c757100abcdd9aeedb89","tid":2181879,"uid":54927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:19:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老味無槍無炮買嗰啲背心把撚咩<br />\n<br />\n有裝備冇咁嘅訓練冇咁嘅知識<br />\n<br />\n着撚到成個海豹咪把撚"},{"pid":"87bad469934a4fba1da269b13ab07090d6b96e6b","tid":2181879,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc36095236ca8ad1abe76c441a9c45b54b96ee24","tid":2181879,"uid":366493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"我睇完 你係想買嚟玩 着上身？<br />\n有關 避彈衣 頭盔 影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ef3D_91MVMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fef3D_91MVMM&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoGdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=b9e89d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ef3D_91MVMM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FGTXzNVhKyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFGTXzNVhKyo&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoGdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=af104c0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FGTXzNVhKyo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"我都有睇過<br />\n我如果係玩就唔會講理防彈板"},{"pid":"033e90c4e0734b5e2dd8280c5c64225f0146df6a","tid":2181879,"uid":370186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eda971f9e0ae0f723941c757100abcdd9aeedb89","tid":2181879,"uid":54927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:19:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老味無槍無炮買嗰啲背心把撚咩<br />\n<br />\n有裝備冇咁嘅訓練冇咁嘅知識<br />\n<br />\n着撚到成個海豹咪把撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"如果佢哋要扮嘅咁就唔會睇呢啲<br />\n如果真係要買晒成身真嘅皮基本幾兩皮走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n有心買真嘅你覺得會唔肯操 <br />\n另外使唔使整埋個訓練日記喺度俾你管住？"},{"pid":"e5a9e0e31294e4528d4b2e4d68072db836583543","tid":2181879,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"da5e470c530c6ced2f47adcf206a5fb11317453e","tid":2181879,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"頭盔後面個個好似叫配重鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287fa4e7386db458fdcd655f81970dc4ee836f8c","tid":2181879,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5e470c530c6ced2f47adcf206a5fb11317453e","tid":2181879,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"頭盔後面個個好似叫配重鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T17:41:22.000Z","msg":"thx!!"},{"pid":"20d744f062f40c45daa50ba70924a5a98759eec1","tid":2181879,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"防彈板 基本上 green tips ammo M855 已經可以打穿III /IV 美軍有部分特種部隊會用呢種子彈"},{"pid":"3596d43a60f5e66371ecc7b7fc1d142a123ace61","tid":2181879,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"巴打寫得幾好<br />\n<br />\n美軍實戰 有次係iraq 單兵要帶20個彈匣 打城市戰<br />\n5個彈匣係絕對唔夠 因為戰鬥可能會被拖長時間"}]}